                            <comment id="28398" author="morrone" created="Fri, 10 Feb 2012 19:10:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You can avoid this problem in the figure by configuring with &quot;--with-o2ib=yes&quot;.  Then it will be really obvious that something went wrong in detecting o2ib, because the build will abort rather than quietly leaving out needed support.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28368" author="cliffw" created="Fri, 10 Feb 2012 13:46:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Tested new build, has o2iblnd&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28341" author="brian" created="Fri, 10 Feb 2012 06:25:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would appear that build #41 resolved this by landing &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-778&quot; title=&quot;RHEL 6.2: rdma_create_id() takes four arguments&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-778&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-778&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Cliff, please confirm and close if so.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28332" author="green" created="Thu, 9 Feb 2012 22:25:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I checked the build log and the configure cannot find something when looking for o2ib.&lt;br/&gt;
Unfortunately we don&apos;t save the config.log, so no way to know it for now, I retriggered the build (#40), so hopefully somebody can grab the config.log from there&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="28329" author="yujian" created="Thu, 9 Feb 2012 21:43:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was introduced by:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-781&quot; title=&quot;Kernel update [RHEL6.2 2.6.32-220.el6]&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-781&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-781&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; kernel: kernel update &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RHEL6.2 2.6.32-220&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The ko2iblnd.ko was in &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/34/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/34/&lt;/a&gt;, but missed from &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/35/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_1/35/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
